==English==
===Etymology===
Shortened form of ''[[atomic bomb]]''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=A-[[bomb]]}}

# An [[atomic bomb]]; a weapon that derives its energy from [[nuclear reaction]]s and has enormous destructive power. Explosion caused by splitting an atom.

====Synonyms====
*[[atom bomb]], [[atomic bomb]], [[fission bomb]], [[nuclear bomb]], [[nuke]] (''slang'')

